<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<html xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd">
    <body>
        <p><span class="SetOffFirstLevel">Merge changes for me </span>Automatically merges changes within the same file that are not part of the same element. If changes have been made to the same element <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Flare">(e.g., the same &lt;p&gt; tag or &lt;h1&gt; tag)</MadCap:conditionalText><MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Lingo">(e.g., the same segment)</MadCap:conditionalText>, <MadCap:variable name="Other.Product" /> will display a prompt to merge the changes using the merge tool.</p>
    </body>
</html>